ore.event
Class EventManager

java.lang.Object
  ore.event.EventManager

public class EventManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class is an adapter between Hibernate entity operations (HibernateListener) and database table operations (TableManger). It provides the mapping between the two by using the Metadata class.
